<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>After Zend_Http_Client supports proxy servers, refactor Zend_Service_Abstract and Zend_Rest_Client to use that feature.  The objective is to allow the user to specify options that are passed to Zend_Http_Client, and that component will utilize the right adapter to support connections via a proxy server.</p>

